  (str ministry) (str `Ministry of Labour and Employment`)
  (str department) (undefined)
  (str longTitle) (str `An Act to provide for the abolition of bonded labour system with a view to preventing the economic and physical exploitation of the weaker sections of the people and for matters connected therewith or incidental thereto.`)
